title: Master paintings from the Hermitage and the State Russian Museum
description:
Master Paintings From the Hermitage and the State Russian Museum, Leningrad
M. Knoedler & Co., Inc. | 1975 | ISBN: N/A | English | 140 pages | PDF | 27 MB


From The Hermitage comes an outstanding selection of paintings by renowned European artists. Although less familiar to us, the paintings by Soviet artists lent by The State Russian Museum are of great interest, because of the quality of the painters whose work is included. Known and honored in their homeland, they may now be studied and admired by a wide audience here
